stomach, but now she felt his his hands slide up to her sides.
But then she sees the wall begin to rush up, closing her optics and covering 
her head with her arms just before they hit.*

" Watch out!"

* But just after she cried that they both hit the wall, sending her right 
into BloodyStrike and taring her from Reptilica's grasp.
Though, this time she ended laying over Bloodystrikes lap, caughing as she 
looked down at his knee.*

" This just isn't my day..."
